{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_05",
  "title": "星見編2章25話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "――朝倉恭一は私の父親なんです\n母とはもうずいぶん前に離婚してますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Van Productions’ president‚ Kyoichi Asakura‚ is my father.\nThough he and my mother divorced a long time ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだったんですの……\n天動さんは、お父様に会うためにバンプロに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ I didn’t know.\nIs that why you joined Van Productions? To meet your father?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.534426496543137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。さあ？\nどうでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Maybe?\nWho knows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.166961606343587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でもあの人は、私と会っても表情一つ変えなくて\n……数年ぶりの再会だっていうのに、酷いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But he didn’t even flinch the first time he met me.\nEven though it was a reunion years in the making. Cruel‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.233628273010247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私は事務所所属のアイドルの一人でしかない\n――娘としては見られていないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am just another idol in his talent agency.\nHe doesn’t see me as a daughter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5711228052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "……これから、お父様との関係を\nどうなさるおつもりなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ how are you going to handle your relationship\nwith your father‚ moving forward?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あの人が無視できなくなるほどの存在に\n――アイドルの頂点に立ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to become so big‚ he can’t ignore me.\nI’m going to be a top idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.35260136234867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "あの人が壁を作るなら、私はそれを乗り越えるだけです\nいえ、壁なんて打ち砕いてやるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If he puts up walls‚ I’ll just jump over them.\nNo‚ I’ll break them down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.01926802901533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……強いんですのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure are strong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.25260136234866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは、強くなければやっていけませんよ\n……自分を信じて突き進むしかないでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols have to be strong.\nYou need to believe in yourself and push through‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8864562284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　その言葉……\nもしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? That phrase…\nCould it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0864562284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ。ありがとうございました\nとても参考になりましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind. Thank you.\nThat was very helpful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2864562283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "お礼を言うのは、スマホを拾ってもらった私の方です\nじゃあ、レッスン頑張ってくださいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should thank you for picking up my phone.\nWell‚ good luck with your lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.45312289504317,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.666666666674,
          "startTime": 73.65312289504318
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "…………壁があるのなら、乗り越える\n……私には……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there’s a wall… jump over it.\nIt’s in my hands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.61978956170984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 80.1453775337
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.41978956170983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すずがまだ帰ってきてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu hasn’t come back yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.28645622837651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はい……こんなに帰りが遅くなること\n今までありませんでしたから、心配で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. She’s never been out\nthis late before. We’re so worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1484063398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nすずとご両親の話し合いって……明日でしたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nSuzu’s talk with her parents is scheduled for tomorrow‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.41666565462947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、すずちゃん\nご両親との話し合いが嫌で、逃げ出したんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that Suzu\nis upset about the talk with her parents and ran away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5100389253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そんなはずない。そう思いながらも）\n（俺の中ですずの母親の言葉がよみがえった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That can’t be. But even as I think this‚)\n(what Suzu’s mother said comes back to me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1100389253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 110.04337225862443
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stgae03.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae03",
      "startTime": 110.04337225862443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すずの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの子は、大きな口ばかり叩きますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl talks a big game‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.17670559195771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すずの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "肝心なところでは、いつも逃げ出してしまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but she always runs away when the going gets tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.676705592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すずの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつかあの子は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someday‚ that girl",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.82670568732514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すずの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あなた方の期待を裏切ることになりますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "will betray all your trust.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4267056873251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.9267056873251
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、{user}くん\nもしかしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}.\nCould it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4267056873251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、すずにゃん探してくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m gonna go look for Suzu-nyan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.79388314864808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。みんなで探しに行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good idea. Let’s all look for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.82172900817568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\n一緒に来てくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re one of us‚ {user}.\nWill you come with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.55506229382524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、当てもなく探して見つかるでしょうか\n警察に通報した方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But can we find her without any clues?\nMaybe we should call the police.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5820169964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nどうしたらいいですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nWhat should we do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.56877512490712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_05-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと待った、{user}くん\n探したり警察に通報する必要はなさそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not so fast‚ {user}.\nI don’t think you need to look for her or call the police anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.96877512490713,
